            <fr:title text="Irrelevant ideal">Irrelevant ideal</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>Given a <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb  N]]></fr:tex>-<fr:link href="hmlg-001L.xml" title="Graded ring" addr="hmlg-001L" type="local">graded ring</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S]]></fr:tex>, its <fr:strong>irrelevant ideal</fr:strong> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathord {\odot }]]></fr:tex> is defined by the subset <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S_+]]></fr:tex> of all positively graded elements.</fr:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
